# Nevora: Transform Warranty and Reliability Data with Ease

Nevora helps you seamlessly convert sales and returns data into Nevada chart format â€” the essential starting point for warranty analysis, survival modeling, and reliability forecasting.  
Built for engineers, analysts, and data scientists who want clean, analysis-ready data without the manual grind.

